data.description: Welcome to this cozy and inviting two bed two bath home conveniently located   minutes away from schools, shopping, dining, and most importantly a short distance to the beach. This is a wonderful place to hang your hat and a great place to call home. The home has an open floor plan great for entertaining.  A nice sized yard to entertainment for both adults and young ones.  Please come check it out for yourself you will not be disappointed.
